{"tid":2322993,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"原來高登執咗我set icon嚟用 仲改咗名做「苦面」","createTime":"2020-12-12T19:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T07:08:32.000Z","uid":30836,"like":118,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8a8601e53b9262495ce1235294e472613ed6ee","tid":2322993,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T19:57:22.000Z","msg":"仲補完咗成set icon 再加多咗好多粒新嘅<br />\n所以可能因為咁改咗做「苦面」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾粒我整得柒咗 放出嚟嗰陣冇留意 所以我認得有部份係我整<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例子：<br />\n原版：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓮燈正版：<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高燈版：<img src=\"https://assets.hkgolden.com/faces/frown/kill.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.hkgolden.com%2Ffaces%2Ffrown%2Fkill.gif&h=a5e55e3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你見到佢開槍嘅時侯塊面有火光咁<br />\n其實係Photoshop export嘅時候我柒咗（不過個效果又唔知點解幾好）<br />\n所以我肯定高燈直接拎咗呢粒嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你牙Joe多謝都冇句<br />\n俾個頭像我都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係蓮囝好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾咗個永久VIP我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735102cbae90d8a8c86512d009672cd000ca8ac3","tid":2322993,"uid":12517,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:03:02.000Z","msg":"咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffd907e6fc9e3d4769ea373d7961f9db89a9599","tid":2322993,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab9936e14feaea76410fc2fe61dfea88c70cd2b","tid":2322993,"uid":894,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T20:04:47.000Z","msg":"舊登仔以後冇得叫依度做抄登<img src=\"/ass